{"type":"message","id":"65e4d4d1","parentId":"e2bf4b2b","timestamp":"2026-03-03T16:22:21.623Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Clarifying Contact Details**\n\nI'm focusing on clarifying how to share contact information. I've re-read the relevant documentation, specifically the SO UL.md and AGENTS.md files, and confirmed the proper method for external communication is through the designated ORION gateway bot email address: `orion_gatewaybot@agentmail.to`. This is distinct from any personal email address, as the documentation emphasizes.\n\n\n**Confirming Contact Method**\n\nI've just revisited the documentation again to solidify the correct response. The user inquired about sharing my email link. I've reconfirmed that `orion_gatewaybot@agentmail.to` is the designated ORION contact method, as specified in the relevant markdown files. I'll craft a reply directly addressing the user's question, keeping a calm and direct tone as is preferred, and share the appropriate address.\n\n\n"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>You can share this inbox identity: `orion_gatewaybot@agentmail.to`.\n\nIt is ORION's AgentMail inbox identity, not a personal mailbox.</final>","textSignature":""}],"api":"google-generative-ai","provider":"google","model":"gemini-2.5-flash-lite","usage":{"input":31366,"output":246,"cacheRead":28921,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31612,"cost":{"input":0.0031366000000000002,"output":0.0000984,"cacheRead":0.0007230250000000001,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003958025}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772554939248}}
