{"type":"message","id":"37843640","parentId":"acf1c851","timestamp":"2026-03-03T16:22:50.119Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Identifying Email Solution**\n\nI'm currently identifying a suitable method to send an email to Alex, informing him of my 10-minute delay for the 3 PM meeting, with a CC to myself. I noticed there's no direct \"email\" tool, so I'm evaluating available tools to see how best to accomplish this.\n\n\n**Evaluating Email Capabilities**\n\nI've determined that the `agentmail` skill is the appropriate tool for sending the email to Alex. My understanding is that this function will need to be executed as a CLI command. I am inferring its usage based on common patterns and hoping it has a syntax similar to `agentmail send --to Alex --subject \"Running late\" --body \" I will be 10 minutes late to our 3pm meeting.\" --cc me`. I'm unsure if it's executable using the `exec` function. I'll need to explore the details of its invocation.\n\n\n**Clarifying Required Email Details**\n\nI've determined I need more information before proceeding with email composition via `agentmail`. I lack both Alex's email and my own for the CC. Additionally, I need to know the meeting context, as the email's details are currently incomplete. I'll focus on clarifying these missing data points before I proceed with crafting the email and executing the command.\n\n\n**Requesting Email Information**\n\nI need Alex's email address and mine for the CC before composing the email with `agentmail`. I've inferred its probable CLI structure and confirmed my lack of address data. I can now ask for the missing details, focusing on obtaining the necessary emails. I'm focusing on acquiring the details I need to start executing the tool.\n\n\n**Requesting Email Details**\n\nI've determined I can't proceed with using the `agentmail` skill without essential details. Although I understand its purpose, I lack crucial contact information, including Alex's email address and my own for the CC. I've confirmed no other tools provide this data. Consequently, I must directly request these email addresses to compose and send the email to Alex. I've prepared a concise and direct question to gather the necessary data.\n\n\n"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>I can help you send that email. Could you please provide:\n\n1.  Alex's email address.\n2.  Your email address (to CC yourself).</final>","textSignature":""}],"api":"google-generative-ai","provider":"google","model":"gemini-2.5-flash-lite","usage":{"input":33172,"output":1198,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34370,"cost":{"input":0.0033172,"output":0.00047920000000000005,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0037964}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772554961062}}
